{
  "stem": "18061.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Take out 11 men and let them work here in that barrack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And somebody's going to ask you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everything is not-- all the people is working what they worked yesterday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, I helped this organize the escape from his brother and from some more people. 11 of them, they escaped by crawling over the fences, that little leaves and grass which was around the barbed wire was taking off [INAUDIBLE] by those people.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he came in, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lalka, ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He asked, is anybody missing here?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I answered, no, the all what worked yesterday, they're here, which was not the same.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then, I was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he came over to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He got me by my head-- I had a head of hair-- and he started knocking on a iron pipe, which I don't know how I didn't feel anything.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was the first time that the [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Lalka ?] touched anybody and left them alive, that time I got with him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Why do you think he let you go?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have no idea why I'm still alive, after going that thing through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were not caught.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What had happened, I find out after I escaped from Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of them came to me, to my home town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He told me that, when they got back, 10 of them got killed by the Poles.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he himself escaped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I met him also in Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His name was Leibish Placefski.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uprising.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The main, I would say, was [INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Horozitski. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a highly educated man, not only with doctor degree, but was very famous also in the Army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was the leader to prepared one uprising.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
